<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">م ت ك:</span> قُرِئَ <span class="c2">«وَأَعْتَدَتْ لَهُنَّ مُتْكًا»</span> .<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْفَرَّاءُ:</span> هُوَ الزُّمَاوَرْدُ.<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الْأَخْفَشُ:</span> هُوَ الْأُتْرُجُّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>